column1: A very special thanks to Mark Ironfield, Morgan Mitchell, PowerFit Gym, The Refuge, Universal Powerlifting Team, Our spotters, loaders
and referees for making this a very well organized event.  There were 50 entrants in this competition. The majority competed raw.
Several new records were set and lifting quality was very good.  PowerFit Gym had some beautiful meet shirts made for the event and they
were the nicest meet shirts I have seen in a very long time.
The APA is planning other events in Peabody and I look forward to the next one.
